UI Description for Claude Code

Overall Style:
Soft, minimal, modern SaaS interface. Feels premium but approachable. Light and airy with generous whitespace.
Background:
Soft gradient — pale pink/lavender to light cream/white. Very subtle, almost pastel. Not flat white, has gentle warmth.
Color Palette:

Background: Soft pink-lavender gradient (#f5f0f5 → #faf8f7)
Cards: White with slight transparency/glassmorphism
Primary accent: Coral/salmon orange (#f08a7a or similar)
Icons: Dark charcoal (#2d2d2d) on light rounded square backgrounds
Text: Dark gray for headings, medium gray for subtext

Typography:

Clean sans-serif (Inter, SF Pro, or similar)
Hero heading: Large, mixed weight — greeting lighter, question bolder
Subtext: Small, muted gray, generous line height

Cards:

Pure white or very subtle transparency
Large border radius (~16-20px)
Very soft drop shadow (barely visible)
Icon in dark rounded square at top left of each card
Title + subtitle beneath icon

Input Bar:

Floating at bottom center
Pill-shaped, white background
Subtle shadow
Icon on left, coral "Send" button on right with arrow
Rounded send button matches accent color

Layout:

Centered content
Logo top left, user avatar top right
Hero content middle (icon, greeting, prompt)
Suggestion cards at bottom in horizontal row
Generous padding everywhere

Vibe:
Clean, calm, inviting. Not sterile — has warmth from the pink tones and coral accent. Premium consumer product feel.